<section class="band-amber">
  <div class="section taproom-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker kicker-ink-2 reveal">The Taproom · 1051 Main Street, Hampton</span>
      <h2 class="display-ink-lg reveal d1">Pull Up<br />A Stool</h2>
      <p class="body-on-ink reveal d1">With twelve taps pouring fresh craft beer and a laid-back patio right on the water, we've got your downtime covered. The weekend tunes are live, the breeze off the river is cool, and the vibe is always easy.</p>
      <p class="body-on-ink reveal d2">Go ahead and bring the whole crew along, too. We're proudly family-friendly, keeping the board games ready, the colouring books out, and plenty of tasty non-alcoholic options on hand to keep the little ones smiling.</p>
      <p class="body-on-ink reveal d2">Whether you're just dropping by for a quick pint or settling in to see what's new on tap, your stool is waiting.</p>
      <div class="stack-buttons reveal d2">
        <a class="btn btn-ink" href="#events">What's On →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="taproom-images reveal d1">
      <img class="photo" src="/assets/photos/bar-chalkboard-menu.webp" alt="Gridiron taproom bar with pendant lights and chalkboard menus" width="724" height="649" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      <img class="photo" src="/assets/photos/three-beers-counter.webp" alt="Three Gridiron pints on the bar counter" width="1164" height="822" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
